432
00:26:33,480 --> 00:26:34,879
Master.

433
00:26:37,520 --> 00:26:38,399
Have you already

434
00:26:39,399 --> 00:26:40,760
met her?

435
00:26:45,720 --> 00:26:46,720
Lingyu,

436
00:26:46,800 --> 00:26:47,960
